==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Unsuccessful
<hw>Un`suc*cess"ful</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos> <def>Not
successful; not producing the desired event; not fortunate; meeting
with, or resulting in, failure; unlucky; unhappy.</def> --
<wordforms><wf>Un`suc*cess"ful*ly</wf>, <pos>adv.</pos> --
<wf>Un`suc*cess"ful*ness</wf>, <pos>n.</pos></wordforms>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Unsufferable</ent>⟦br⟧
